      <title>意大利副总理萨尔维尼在移民案中无罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/italy-s-deputy-premier-salvini-found-not-guilty-in-migrant-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利副总理马泰奥·萨尔维尼 (Matteo Salvini) 因 2019 年阻止一艘载有 147 名移民的救援船停靠西西里岛而被宣判无罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/italy-s-deputy-premier-salvini-found-not-guilty-in-migrant-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
